<DOC><DOCNO> WSJ870206-0077 </DOCNO><HL> Sunshine Mining Extends Offer</HL><DD> 02/06/87</DD><SO> WALL STREET JOURNAL (J)</SO><IN> SSCBUYBACKS, REDEMPTIONS, SWAP OFFERS (BBK) </IN><DATELINE> DALLAS  </DATELINE><TEXT>   Sunshine Mining Co. said it extended to Feb. 20 its exchange offer for interests in 38 drilling programs of its Woods Petroleum Corp. unit. The offer was set to expire today.    The mining concern said that through yesterday it had been tendered interests representing $4.7 million in exchange value. Sunshine is seeking to exchange common stock for half the interest in the programs, whose total value is about $37 million. </TEXT></DOC>